Angel Prime




he flys over and in the middle left side of FZ and Ironraptor he then opens 
a com to all so everyone could here.


Angel Prime:




"no we will not bow down to your commands. Ironraptor you are weak. you 
would let your guard down so Zardus and the alliance can stabbs us in the 
back. no the maximals will never fall not today not ever. To all maximals 
this is Angel Prime. you have two choices give up everything you ever fought 
for and all you dreams and hopes so the Alliance can walk over us. Or you 
can push back and fight the alliance to the bloody end. and go out with some 
pride. Ironraptor is not the leader she wants was. lets not fail."


Angel Prime flys up and opens his wing wide and starts firiing little fire 
like rain but it pure fire.




[just to point this out on behalf os Soulstice. she has a point you notice 
that every time the alliance attack the maximals they lose. The ark got 
destroyed by them.]
